cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.AI 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques applied to medical data, specifically radiology reports. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also uses word embeddings, which are a popular technique in machine learning, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category. The paper also deals with information retrieval (IR) and computer vision (CV) to some extent, so cs.IR and cs.CV are also possible categories. Finally, the paper uses deep learning techniques, which are a subset of artificial intelligence (AI), so cs.AI is also a possible category.
